  "description": "Non-profit religious-corp actor that curates public-interest / public-sector information (government PR, 独立行政法人, 公益法人, 官報) into faithful summaries with provenance and publishes social briefings to app-aozora. Containment (organizer sealed) + independent PublicInfoGovernor + append-only briefing ledger + registry whitelist (only registered public-sector/public-interest sources). Autonomous publication per ADR-2606281500 (種をまく); aggregate-first (1 run = 1 briefing). Inference on the Murakumo fleet. Real-LLM deploy live-verified against Ollama gemma-4-E4B.",
  "descriptionJa": "公益・国営団体（政府広報・独立行政法人・公益法人・官報）の news/情報を整理して app-aozora に social post する actor。封じ込め（organizer）+ 独立 PublicInfoGovernor + append-only briefing 台帳 + registry ホワイトリスト。投稿は ADR-2606281500（種をまく）で自律。aggregate-first。",
